       aGroupPerf1DayIntervalMoniSecs."
     REFERENCE
       "[TR-159], Section 5.5.1.64"
     ::= { g9982PortPm1DayEntry 2 }

   g9982PortPm1DayIntervalRxErrors  OBJECT-TYPE
